{"tid":435462,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"昨日地鐵事件 E-mail 此主題給朋友","createTime":"2017-10-14T09:56:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T10:43:50.000Z","uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"56741f2e75890527556d21a07ec784406b034b6d","tid":435462,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T09:56:31.000Z","msg":"如常6點放工，又要同人逼車返屋企，係九龍塘依舊多人到想死，咁啱有個女仔約望20歲左右，著短衫牛仔褲，少少可愛路線咁，個陣都無咩野，望兩眼就算，排到第二架車終於上到車，我同佢都同時間慢慢咁被後面既人推上車，去到門口位都幾乎無得再逼，點鬼知有兩個好似大陸既阿嬸又要死逼入黎，搞到我同個女仔痴到實一實，佢被人逼到patpat痴實我下面，我緊係即刻講唔好意思，佢搖頭話唔緊要，我係度苦笑，終於開車，個大陸婆又係度死郁，再加上車既郁動，我小弟弟真係不知不覺越黎越硬，我想郁都郁唔到，成程車就咁樣去到下站，好彩前面個女仔無野乍！"},{"pid":"21af08042af2c7d7948a4eb5d2d3ed5ee6c85329","tid":435462,"uid":145959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T09:58:17.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"f84794d72c5520b41b567785cf7b6549335a7ea1","tid":435462,"uid":44044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:01:29.000Z","msg":"咁你有無射"},{"pid":"38a656c78a3f9cedb83cacb8f654373ec23f4a71","tid":435462,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:08:05.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"44e77ccabf1f10fa25662983122b7f0850234d63","tid":435462,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:08:55.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"66fe03c0d10d4242860c04e173b66847fdff872a","tid":435462,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:37:55.000Z","msg":"成班酸撚"},{"pid":"7e0cf8c11668a48d24a41904c0e9972082d65007","tid":435462,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:40:43.000Z","msg":"向上水方向&zwnj;？"},{"pid":"955e4814b03ff35ef5026adb98da87b3d40085ea","tid":435462,"uid":92095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成班酸撚</blockquote><br />\n又無人正負評又無人屌你又剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b2aa86a86debef952f2d8bb655166404ab03d7","tid":435462